{"about_the_game":"<u><strong>What is Realm Of Cubes?</strong></u><br>Realm Of Cubes is a Voxel-based Action Adventure RPG. It takes place in a fantasy world that is in need of help from you, the adventurer. You can experience the world by yourself, or with a friend! <br><u><strong>What features are in the game?</strong></u><br>\u25fdDo Quest!<br>\u25fdLevel Up!<br>\u25fdChoose between seven classes: Mage, Paladin, Ranger, Rogue, Warrior, Deathknight, Shaman.<br>\u25fdExplore a hand crafted fantasy world inspired by World of Warcraft and Cube World.<br>\u25fdAction based combat with aiming/strafing.<br>\u25fdDifferent mounts and achievments to collect!<br>\u25fdLots of companion pets to find!<br>\u25fdHang gliding!<br>\u25fdHelp out the residents by completing quest and defeating monsters around the world!<br>\u25fdUnique talent trees for each class.<br>\u25fdLevel progression up to level 60.<br>\u25fdPlay single player or with a friend with couch co-op!<br>\u25fdLots of unique spell abilities for each class!<br>\u25fdMultiple professions: Bartending, Cooking, Smelting, Tailoring, Alchemy, Camping, Blacksmithing, Fishing, Mining, and Gardening!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1992940/extras/DeathKnightGif1.gif?t=1688614640\" /><br><br>However, be careful, <strong>if you start the game with a controller</strong>. Steam tries to map the keyboard and mouse to a controller and it's supposed to be played with a keyboard and mouse. If you would like to play it with couch co-op <strong>here's a guide I'm linking below</strong>.<br><br>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1992940/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1688614640","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1992940/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1688614640","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1992940/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=168